系列以1995年[[超级任天堂|超级任天堂]]游戏《[[幻想传说|幻想传说]]》诞生，该作引入并确立了传说系列的许多元素<ref name="YTtales" />。游戏到2006年才以[[Game_Boy_Advance|Game Boy Advance]]版登录西方。游戏还移植于[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]、[[PlayStation_Portable|PlayStation Portable]]和[[iOS|iOS]]<ref name="bare_url" /><ref name="bare_url_a">{{cite web |url=http://psp.ign.com/articles/732/732428p1.html |author=Alfonso, Andrew |title=Tales of Phantasia Playtest – PlayStation Portable Preview at IGN |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2006-09-12 |accessdate=2012-08-18 |archive-date=2009-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090415135618/http://psp.ign.com/articles/732/732428p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Bandai Namco Pulling 'Tales of Phantasia' on iOS, Will Become "Unusable" on August 28th|url=http://toucharcade.com/2014/07/07/bandai-namco-pulling-tales-of-phantasia-on-ios/|publisher=Touch Arcade|author=Nelson, Jarad|date=2014-07-07|accessdate=2014-08-13|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015122/https://toucharcade.com/2014/07/07/bandai-namco-pulling-tales-of-phantasia-on-ios/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。PlayStation有上有两部传说游戏首发：1997年的《[[宿命传说|宿命传说]]》，也最早在北美发行的作品<ref name="rpgfan">{{cite web |url=http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/talesofdestiny/Tales_of_Destiny.html |title=RPGFan Reviews – Tales of Destiny |publisher=Rpgfan.com |date= |accessdate=2012-08-18 |archive-date=2012-12-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Cz1saGJu?url=http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/talesofdestiny/Tales_of_Destiny.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；2000年的《[[永恒传说|永恒传说]]》，在西元2001年以《宿命传说2》为题发行<ref name="ToD2interview">{{cite web |title=Tales of Destiny 2 Interview |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2001/06/08/tales-of-destiny-2-interview |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |accessdate=2013-06-19 |date=2001-06-08}}</ref>。

五部作品在[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]发行。《宿命传说》的直系续作《[[宿命传说2|宿命传说2]]》于2001年发行，2007年发行日本PlayStation Portable版；PlayStation 2原版是唯一中文化的游戏<ref name="gnn" />，而双版本都未在西方发行<ref name="bare_url_c">{{cite web |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2002/12/02/tales-of-destiny-2-hands-on |title=Tales of Destiny 2 Hands-On – PlayStation 2 Preview at IGN |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |author=IGN Staff |date=2002-12-02 |accessdate=2012-08-18 |archive-date=2014-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220053034/http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/12/02/tales-of-destiny-2-hands-on |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ToD2psp">{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2007/02/15/a-tale-of-more-tales|title=A Tale of More Tales|author=Gantayat, Anoop|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2007-02-15|accessdate=2014-08-13}}</ref>。《[[仙乐传说|仙乐传说]]》在日本PlayStation 2和[[任天堂GameCube|任天堂GameCube]]发行，其中GameCube版登陆北美和欧洲<ref name="NGC dates">{{cite web |title=Tales of Symphonia Update |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/tales-of-symphonia-update/1100-6101456/ |author=Massimilla, Bethany |date=2004-06-25 |accessdate=2012-05-02 |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425040730/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/tales-of-symphonia-update/1100-6101456/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="SymphPS2">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/symphonia-to-include-tales-of-rebirth-preview/1100-6101680/|title=Symphonia to include Tales of Rebirth preview|author=Niizumi, Hirohiko|publisher=[[Gamespot|Gamespot]]|date=2004-06-30|accessdate=2014-08-13|archive-date=2020-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629071202/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/symphonia-to-include-tales-of-rebirth-preview/1100-6101680/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这是系列首部采用[[三维计算机图形|3D]]角色与环境的作品，也是首部在欧洲发行的作品<ref name="YTtales" /><ref name="GamaInterview" />。《重生传说》于2004年发行<ref name="autogenerated2004">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/12/16/tales-of-rebirth-early-impressions |title=Tales of Rebirth Early Impressions |publisher=IGN |date=2004-12-16 |accessdate=2013-02-21 |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425040741/https://www.ign.com/articles/2004/12/16/tales-of-rebirth-early-impressions |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2008年移植到PlayStation Portable，尚未在日本外本地化<ref name="JoyLocalRebirth">{{cite web |last=McElroy |first=Justin |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2007/07/20/new-tales-coming-to-ps2-psp-wii-and-ds-in-japan/ |title=New Tales coming to PS2, PSP, Wii and DS in Japan |publisher=Joystiq |date=2007-07-20 |accessdate=2012-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012182346/http://www.joystiq.com/2007/07/20/new-tales-coming-to-ps2-psp-wii-and-ds-in-japan/ |archive-date=2007-10-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。《[[遗迹传说|遗迹传说]]》和《[[深渊传说|深渊传说]]》皆于2005年在日本发行，并双双在次年北美本地化<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/games/tales-of-legendia/ps2-718856 |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2013-07-04 |title=Tales of Legenda - PlayStation 2 |archive-date=2018-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180110110303/http://www.ign.com/games/tales-of-legendia/ps2-718856 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/tales-of-the-abyss/reviews/tales-of-the-abyss-review-6159629/ |title=Tales of the Abyss Review |publisher=GameSpot.com |date=2006-10-10 |accessdate=2012-08-19 |archive-date=2019-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608095649/https://www.gamespot.com/tales-of-the-abyss/reviews/tales-of-the-abyss-review-6159629/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《遗迹传说》是首部且唯一由南梦宫内部团队“Project Melfes”开发的传说游戏<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/12/10/new-tales-game |title=New Tales Game |publisher=IGN |author=Gantayat, Anoop |date=2004-12-09 |accessdate=2012-06-07 |archive-date=2013-06-16 |archive-url=https://archive.li/20130616005640/http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/12/10/new-tales-game |dead-url=no }}</ref>，《深渊传说》则由《仙乐传说》团队开发，使用了相同的图形引擎<ref name="GamaInterview" />。《深渊传说》随后移植到[[任天堂3DS|任天堂3DS]]，在日本、北美和欧洲发行<ref name="3DS">{{Cite web|url=http://andriasang.com/compmg/tales_of_the_abyss_3ds/|title=Tales of the Abyss Set for 3DS|author=Gantayat, Anoop|date=2010-09-29|publisher=Andriasang.com|accessdate=2010-09-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724121537/http://andriasang.com/compmg/tales_of_the_abyss_3ds/|archivedate=2014-07-24|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="NE">{{cite web |url=http://nintendoeverything.com/93196/namco-bandai-considers-tales-of-the-abyss-a-success-in-europe/ |title=Namco Bandai considers Tales of the Abyss a success in Europe |publisher=Nintendo Everything |date=2012-07-12 |accessdate=2013-06-10 |author=Brian }}{{Dead link|date=2018年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref>。

《[[圣洁传说|圣洁传说]]》于2007年在日本任天堂DS平台发行<ref name="bare_url_d">{{cite web |url=http://ds.gamespy.com/nintendo-ds/tales-of-innocence/ |title=Tales of Innocence – Nintendo DS – GameSpy |publisher=Ds.gamespy.com |date=2007-12-03 |accessdate=2012-08-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100710231445/http://ds.gamespy.com/nintendo-ds/tales-of-innocence/ |archivedate=2010-07-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，重制版《圣洁传说R》于2012年在[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]平台发行<ref name="rpgfan_b">{{cite web |url=http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/Tales_of_Innocence_R/index.html |title=RPGFan Review – Tales of Innocence R |publisher=Rpgfan.com |date= |accessdate=2012-08-19 |archive-date=2019-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604234020/http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/Tales_of_Innocence_R/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；两个版本都未在西方发行<ref name="InnocenceLocal">{{cite web |author=Name * |url=http://www.technologytell.com/gaming/53707/important-importables-notable-fan-translation-projects/ |title=Important Importables: Notable fan translation projects |4=GamerTell |publisher=Technologytell.com |date=2012-01-17 |accessdate=2012-08-19 |archive-date=2014-09-08 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SQY5P406?url=http://www.technologytell.com/gaming/53707/important-importables-notable-fan-translation-projects/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[游戏机历史_(第七世代)|第七世代游戏机]]上的首款游戏是《[[薄暮传说|薄暮传说]]》，对应[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]平台，2008年在日本和北美、2009年在欧洲发行<ref name="releasedategamespot">{{cite web| url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2008/08/07/tales-of-vesperia-launches-in-japan | title=Tales of Vesperia Launches in Japan |author=Gantayat, Anoop | publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2008-08-07 |accessdate=2014-08-13}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=Tales of Vesperia | publisher=Bandai Namco | url=http://www.bandainamcogames.eu/product/tales-of-vesperia/xbox-360 | accessdate=2014-08-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819084935/http://www.bandainamcogames.eu/product/tales-of-vesperia/xbox-360 | archive-date=2014-08-19 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/tales-of-vesperia-hits-europe-in-june |title=Tales of Vesperia hits Europe in JuneTales of Vesperia hits Europe in June |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |author=Bramwell, Tom |date=2009-03-25 |accessdate=2009-09-23 |archive-date=2015-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722052436/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/tales-of-vesperia-hits-europe-in-june |dead-url=no }}</ref>。日本独占PlayStation 3移植版也于2009年发行<ref>{{cite web |author=Goldman, Tom |url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/94556-Japanese-Tales-of-Vesperia-Fans-Upset-Over-PS3-Port |title=Japanese Tales of Vesperia Fans Upset Over PS3 Port |publisher=Escapist Magazine |date=2009-09-09 |accessdate=2012-08-19 |archive-date=2019-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605062527/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/94556-Japanese-Tales-of-Vesperia-Fans-Upset-Over-PS3-Port |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[心灵传说|心灵传说]]》于2008年在任天堂DS平台发行<ref name="siliconera">{{cite web |author=Spencer |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2012/02/22/tales-of-hearts-trademark-filed-by-namco-bandai-in-the-us/ |title=Tales of Hearts Trademark Filed By Namco Bandai in the US |publisher=Siliconera |date=2012-02-22 |accessdate=2012-08-20 |archive-date=2019-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190530141916/https://www.siliconera.com/2012/02/22/tales-of-hearts-trademark-filed-by-namco-bandai-in-the-us/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，重制版《心灵传说R》于2013年在日本、2014年年在西方发行<ref name="IGNorigins" /><ref name="KotakuHearts">{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5970701/tales-of-hearts-r-is-shaping-up-to-be-the-definitive-version-of-the-game|title=Tales of Hearts R is Shaping Up To Be The Definitive Version of the Game|author=Eisenbeis, Richard|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|date=2012-12-22|accessdate=2014-07-24|archive-date=2018-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180705033245/https://kotaku.com/5970701/tales-of-hearts-r-is-shaping-up-to-be-the-definitive-version-of-the-game|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

第12作《[[圣恩传说|圣恩传说]]》于2009年在日本[[Wii|Wii]]平台发行<ref name="FJP date">{{cite web |url=http://andriasang.com/comozw/tales_of_graces_f_date/ |title=Date Set for Tales of Graces F |first=Anoop |last=Gantayat |date=2010-09-07 |publisher=Andriasang.com |accessdate=2012-05-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004224930/http://andriasang.com/comozw/tales_of_graces_f_date/ |archivedate=2013-10-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。PlayStation 3移植版《圣恩传说f》于2009年在日本、2012年在西方发行<ref name="FJP date" /><ref name="IGN review">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/03/20/tales-of-graces-f-review-un-scored |title=''Tales of Graces f'' IGN review |first=Ryan |last=Clements |date=2012-03-20 |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2012-05-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140320055005/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/03/20/tales-of-graces-f-review-un-scored |archivedate=2014-03-20 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="EU date">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004234548/http://www.uk.namcobandaigames.eu/news/2012/05/16/namco-bandai-games-unveils-tales-of-graces-f-day-one-edition-content-and-launch-date/2819 |archivedate=2013-10-04 |url=http://www.uk.namcobandaigames.eu/news/2012/05/16/namco-bandai-games-unveils-tales-of-graces-f-day-one-edition-content-and-launch-date/2819 |title=Namco Bandai Games unveils ''Tales of Graces f'' Day One Edition content and launch date! |date=2011-05-16 |publisher=[[Namco_Bandai_Games|Namco Bandai Games]] |accessdate=2012-05-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。系列15周年纪念作品《[[无尽传说|无尽传说]]》于2011年在日本PlayStation 3<ref name="IGNanniversary">{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2013/06/07/talking-tales-of-xillia-with-hideo-baba|title=Talking Tales of Xillia with Hideo Baba|author=Kamen, Mat|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2013-06-07|accessdate=2014-07-24}}</ref><ref name="Release date">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724162130/http://andriasang.com/comvx5/tales_xillia_date/ |archivedate=2014-07-24 |url=http://andriasang.com/comvx5/tales_xillia_date/ |title=''Tales of Xillia'' Dated, Gets Special PS3 |first=Anoop |last=Gantayat |date=2011-05-29 |publisher=Andriasang.com |accessdate=2013-05-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、2013年在西方发行<ref name="NA date gem">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308102929/http://gematsu.com/2013/04/tales-of-xillia-us-release-date-set |archivedate=2014-03-08 |url=http://gematsu.com/2013/04/tales-of-xillia-us-release-date-set |title=''Tales of Xillia'' U.S. release date set |first=Sal |last=Romano |date=2013-04-05 |publisher=Gematsu.com |accessdate=2013-05-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="EU collectors">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724162409/http://www.bandainamcogames.eu/news/2013/04/11/namco-bandai-games-announce-the-release-date-pre-order-program-and-collector-s-edition-of-tales-of-xillia/3461 |archivedate=2014-07-24 |url=http://www.uk.namcobandaigames.eu/news/2013/04/11/namco-bandai-games-announce-the-release-date-pre-order-program-and-collector-s-edition-of-tales-of-xillia/3461 |title=Namco Bandai Games announce the release date, pre-order program and Collector's Edition of ''Tales of Xillia'' |date=2013-04-11 |publisher=[[Namco_Bandai_Games_Europe|Namco Bandai Games Europe]] |accessdate=2013-05-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。其直系续作《[[无尽传说2|无尽传说2]]》是系列第14部正篇，于2012年在日本、2014年在西方发行<ref>{{cite web |author=Ishaan . 2 June 2012 . 10:13am |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2012/06/02/tales-of-xillia-2-trailer-shows-characters-choices-and-battles/ |title=Tales of Xillia 2 Trailer Shows Characters, Choices And Battles |publisher=Siliconera |date=2012-06-02 |accessdate=2012-08-20 |archive-date=2019-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607213111/https://www.siliconera.com/2012/06/02/tales-of-xillia-2-trailer-shows-characters-choices-and-battles/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Spencer . 9 August 2012 . 1:48am |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2012/08/09/tales-of-xillia-2s-gorgeous-modern-world/ |title=Tales of Xillia 2's Gorgeous Modern World |publisher=Siliconera |date=2012-08-09 |accessdate=2012-08-20 |archive-date=2019-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190615161015/https://www.siliconera.com/2012/08/09/tales-of-xillia-2s-gorgeous-modern-world/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://gematsu.com/2013/07/tales-of-xillia-2-coming-west-in-2014 |title=Tales of Xillia 2 coming west in 2014 |last1=Romano |first1=Sal |date=2013-07-06 |website=Gematsu |publisher= |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927115522/https://www.gematsu.com/2013/07/tales-of-xillia-2-coming-west-in-2014 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第15部正篇《[[热情传说|热情传说]]》2015年在全球发行<ref name="IGNorigins" /><ref name="ZestYears" />，但故事被不少玩家批評，到2016年發售作為熱情傳說前傳的《[[緋夜傳奇|緋夜傳奇]]》。4年後於2019年E3展發表正篇系列新作《[[破曉傳奇|破曉傳奇]]》的消息，作為系列的25週年紀念作名義在[[PlayStation|Playstation]], [[Xbox_Series_X/S|Xbox Series X/S]] 及[[Steam|Steam]]於2021年全球發行。

==== 续作与衍生作品 ====

系列有少量续作和大量衍生作品与子系列。《风雨传说》属于例外，由多名正篇创作人制作，是《圣洁传说》的先行者，这是衍生作品而非原作品<ref name="gamespot.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/tales-of-the-tempest-delayed-in-japan-6147166 |title=Tales of the Tempest delayed in Japan |publisher=GameSpot.com |date=2006-10-26 |accessdate=2012-08-23}}</ref><ref name="TalesFamitsuYoshizumi">{{cite web|url=http://www.famitsu.com/interview/article/2007/08/01/668,1185955758,76180,0,0.html|title=『テイルズ オブ』シリーズ総合プロデューサー吉積信氏に直撃！|publisher=[[Famitsu|Famitsu]]|date=2008-08-03|accessdate=2014-08-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140213223510/http://www.famitsu.com/interview/article/2007/08/01/668,1185955758,76180,0,0.html|archivedate=2014-02-13|deadurl=no}}</ref>。直系续作有三部：《宿命传说2》、《无尽传说2》和《[[仙乐传说_-拉塔特斯克的骑士-|仙乐传说 -拉塔特斯克的骑士-]]》<ref name="IGNorigins" />。《永恒传说》有一部[[Microsoft_Windows|PC平台]]衍生[[大型多人在线角色扮演游戏|大型多人在线角色扮演游戏]]《[[永恒传说Online|永恒传说Online]]》<ref name="ToEOrpggamer">{{cite web|url=http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q3-2005/091205a.html|title=Namco, Bandai Reveal Tokyo Game Show Lineups|author=Ferris, Nick; Beck, Adrienne|publisher=RPGamer|date=2005-09-12|accessdate=2014-07-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130705075307/http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q3-2005/091205a.html|archivedate=2013-07-05|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。手机平台有多部跨界作品，如《Tales of Link》、[[Tales_of_Mobile|Tales of Mobile]]系列、《Tales of Card Evolve》、《Tales of Kizna》和《群星傳奇》<ref>{{cite web |first=Emily |last=Gera |url=http://www.polygon.com/2013/8/27/4663038/tales-of-link-coming-to-mobile-in-japan |title=Tales of Link coming to mobile in Japan |publisher=Polygon |date=2013-08-01 |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041000/https://www.polygon.com/2013/8/27/4663038/tales-of-link-coming-to-mobile-in-japan |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ToMwebsite">{{cite web|url=http://www.talesweb.com/mobile/products/index.html|title=Tales Of Mobile -テイルズ オブ モバイル-|publisher=[[Bandai_Namco|Bandai Namco]], Official Website|accessdate=2014-07-24|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116141313/http://www.talesweb.com/mobile/products/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ANNasteria">{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-02-17/tales-of-asteria-mobile-game-unites-tales-of-characters-this-spring|title=Tales of Asteria Mobile Game Unites Tales of Characters This Spring|publisher=|date=2014-02-17|accessdate=2014-07-24|archive-date=2020-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041109/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-02-17/tales-of-asteria-mobile-game-unites-tales-of-characters-this-spring|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="SilLocalInterview" />。两部作品于日本PlayStation Portable平台发行：2009年的《[[对战传说|对战传说]]》和2012年的《[[英雄傳奇_閃耀雙星|英雄傳奇 閃耀雙星]]》<ref name="PSP Hyper">{{cite web |title=Tales of VS. Getting Early August Release In Japan? |url=http://www.psphyper.com/psp/tales-of-vs-getting-early-august-release-in-japan/ |date=2009-05-14 |work= |publisher=PSP Hyper |accessdate=2009-07-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090518140121/http://www.psphyper.com/psp/tales-of-vs-getting-early-august-release-in-japan/ |archivedate=2009-05-18 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Ishaan . 23 February 2012 . 8:30am |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2012/02/23/tales-of-the-heroes-twin-brave-has-a-nice-opening-theme/ |title=Tales of the Heroes: Twin Brave Has A Nice Opening Theme |publisher=Siliconera |date=2012-02-23 |accessdate=2013-07-11 |archive-date=2019-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629060947/https://www.siliconera.com/2012/02/23/tales-of-the-heroes-twin-brave-has-a-nice-opening-theme/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。世界传说是主要的衍生子系列，首作《[[世界传说_换装迷宫|世界传说 换装迷宫]]》于2000年在日本Game Boy Color平台发行<ref name="ReferenceC">{{cite web|last=Gifford|first=Kevin|title=Two Tales of Phantasia Remakes Hitting PSP|url=http://www.1up.com/news/tales-phantasia-remakes-hitting-psp|publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|date=2010-03-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413183623/http://www.1up.com/news/tales-phantasia-remakes-hitting-psp|archivedate=2014-04-13|deadurl=yes|accessdate=2015-01-13}}</ref>。只有《[[世界传说_光明神话|世界传说 光明神话]]》在西方发行<ref name="ReferenceA">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/tales-of-the-world-radiant-mythology/ |title=Tales of the World: Radiant Mythology |publisher=GameSpot.com |date=2007-07-17 |accessdate=2012-08-23 |archive-date=2019-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611120818/https://www.gamespot.com/tales-of-the-world-radiant-mythology/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一子系列传说迷传说有两部作品，分别于2002年在PlayStation、2007年在PlayStation 2平台发行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/tales-of-fandom-vol-1/ |title=Tales of Fandom Vol. 1 |publisher=GameSpot.com |date=2002-01-31 |accessdate=2012-08-23 |archive-date=2019-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629044422/https://www.gamespot.com/tales-of-fandom-vol-1/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/tales-of-fandom-vol-2/ |title=Tales of Fandom Vol. 2 |publisher=GameSpot.com |date=2007-06-28 |accessdate=2012-08-23 |archive-date=2019-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629053146/https://www.gamespot.com/tales-of-fandom-vol-2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 相关媒体 ===

传说系列有扩展到广播剧、漫画和动画等媒体。多部传说游戏有改编[[原创动画录影带|原创动画录影带]]（OVA）和电视连剧续。《仙乐传说》OVA三集于2007年到2011年放映，后于2013年发布合辑<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2013-06-01/tales-of-symphonia/unisonant-pack-hd-remaster-bundles-original-symphonia-sequel |title=Tales of Symphonia Unisonant Pack announced |date=2013-06-01 |publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |accessdate=2013-06-02 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108222124/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2013-06-01/tales-of-symphonia/unisonant-pack-hd-remaster-bundles-original-symphonia-sequel |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《深渊传说》改编电视连续剧于2008年10月至2009年3月播出<ref>{{cite web |script-title=ja:テイルズ オブ ジ アビス公式サイト |url=http://www.tv-toa.jp/ |publisher=TV-TOA.com |language=ja |accessdate=2008-07-07 |archive-date=2012-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120427055257/http://www.tv-toa.jp/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《幻想传说》和《永恒传说》也有改编动画<ref name="TalesAnime">{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-06-14/tales-of-the-abyss-anime-reportedly-in-the-works|title=Tales of the Abyss Anime Reportedly in the Works|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=2008-06-16|accessdate=2014-07-24|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108083638/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-06-14/tales-of-the-abyss-anime-reportedly-in-the-works|dead-url=no}}</ref>。系列首部戏剧片是《薄暮传说》前传《[[薄暮传说_首鸣|薄暮传说 首鸣]]》于2009年在日本、2012年在北美上映<ref name="animenewsnetwork">{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-04-02/funimation-adds-tales-of-vesperia-anime-film |title=Funimation Adds Tales of Vesperia Anime Film – News |publisher=Anime News Network |date= |accessdate=2012-08-19 |archive-date=2015-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005190009/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-04-02/funimation-adds-tales-of-vesperia-anime-film |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《热情传说》的电视动画也处于制作期<ref name="ANNfestival">{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-05-31/tales-of-zestiria-game-gets-tv-anime-special-by-ufotable/.75074|title=Tales of Zestiria Game Gets TV Anime Special by ufotable|author=|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=2014-05-31|accessdate=2014-05-31|archive-date=2015-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005051105/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-05-31/tales-of-zestiria-game-gets-tv-anime-special-by-ufotable/.75074|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最新作《破曉傳說》於2020年12月釋出動畫PV。

系列还有书籍和[[日本广播剧|广播剧]]作品。《幻想传说》有多张广播剧，包括2000年1月和3月发行的四张选辑<ref>{{cite web |url=http://vgmdb.net/album/17625 |publisher=VGMdb |accessdate=2013-07-08 |title=MACM-1094 Drama CD Tales of Phantasia ~ANTHOLOGY. 1~ |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041115/https://vgmdb.net/album/17625 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://vgmdb.net/album/8437 |publisher=VGMdb |accessdate=2013-07-08 |title=MACM-1095 Drama CD Tales of Phantasia ~ANTHOLOGY. 2~ |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041117/https://vgmdb.net/album/8437 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和2001年12月发行的独立广播剧<ref>{{cite web|url=http://vgmdb.net/album/8482|publisher=VGMdb|accessdate=2013-07-08|title=MACM-1144 Tales of Phantasia Chara Talk CD ~PANIC-WORLD~|archive-date=2020-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041220/https://vgmdb.net/album/8482|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《仙乐传说》也有七张讲述游戏剧情的广播剧<ref name="CDs">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104220753/http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=21&category=2 |archivedate=2013-11-04 |url=http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=21&category=2 |title=''Tales of Symphonia'' CD releases |publisher=[[Namco_Bandai_Games|Namco Bandai Games]] |language=ja |accessdate=2012-05-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《遗迹传说》的两张广播剧分别于2005年8月和9月发行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://vgmdb.net/album/1121 |title=AVCA-22915/B Tales of Legendia ~voice of character quest~ 1 |publisher=VGMdb |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929052327/https://vgmdb.net/album/1121 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://vgmdb.net/album/1122 |title=AVCA-22966~7/B Tales of Legendia ~voice of character quest~ 2 |publisher=VGMdb |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120085951/https://vgmdb.net/album/1122 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《幻想传说》的漫画于2008至2009年间连载<ref>{{cite web| script-title=ja:テイルズオブファンタジア 1 | publisher= 角川書店 | author=MAKOTO2号 | year=2009|isbn=978-4-04-715232-8 | language=ja}}</ref>，《深渊传说》发售同年也有三卷改编漫画发行<ref name="Third Manga">{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2009-04-03/tales-of-the-abyss-manga-to-launch-this-month |title=Tales of the Abyss Manga to Launch This Month |publisher=Anime News Network |date=2009-04-03 |accessdate=2009-04-03 |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041231/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2009-04-03/tales-of-the-abyss-manga-to-launch-this-month |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《仙乐传说》被小说化与漫画化<ref name="Books">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104220836/http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=21&category=1 |archivedate=2013-11-04 |url=http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=21&category=1 |title=''Tales of Symphonia'' book releases |publisher=[[Namco_Bandai_Games|Namco Bandai Games]] |language=ja |accessdate=2012-05-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《宿命传说》、《圣恩传说》和《无尽传说》也有此类改编作品<ref>{{cite web |url=http://vgmdb.net/album/779 |publisher=VGMdb |accessdate=2013-07-02 |title=MACM-1092 Tales of Destiny ~PROUST~ Forgotten Chronicle |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041149/https://vgmdb.net/album/779 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ToG Books">{{cite web |url=http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=131&category=1 |title=''Tales of Graces'' book releases |publisher=[[Namco_Bandai_Games|Namco Bandai Games]] |language=ja |accessdate=2012-05-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140315214427/http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=131&category=1 |archivedate=2014-03-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="ToG CDs">{{cite web |url=http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=131&category=2 |title=''Tales of Graces'' CD releases |publisher=[[Namco_Bandai_Games|Namco Bandai Games]] |language=ja |accessdate=2012-05-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140315132316/http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=131&category=2 |archivedate=2014-03-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="ToX Books">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130317111440/http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=259&category=1 |archivedate=2013-03-17 |url=http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=259&category=1 |title=''Tales of Xillia'' book releases |publisher=[[Namco_Bandai_Games|Namco Bandai Games]] |language=ja |accessdate=2013-05-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="ToX CDs">{{cite web |url=http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=259&category=2 |title=''Tales of Xillia'' CD releases |publisher=[[Namco_Bandai_Games|Namco Bandai Games]] |language=ja |accessdate=2013-05-05 |archive-date=2014-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220030221/http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/goods/title.php?title=259&category=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 共通元素 ==

=== 玩法 ===

传说系列属于[[电子角色扮演游戏|电子角色扮演游戏]]系列。许多元素一作又一作的继承。系列最大特征元素是战斗系统“線性動作戰鬥系統”（LMBS）。它被视作每部正篇的支柱与基础，自首作《幻想传说》引入以来，多次强化或改动<ref name="1upBabaInterview">{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/features/tales-xillia-director-hideo-baba|title=Tales of Xillia Director Hideo Baba on the Ever-Changing RPG Landscape|author=Mackey, Bob|publisher=[[1Up.com|1Up.com]]|date=2013-01-21|accessdate=2014-07-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513044557/http://www.1up.com/features/tales-xillia-director-hideo-baba|archivedate=2013-05-13|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。系统采用类似打斗的即时战斗系统，全然不同于《幻想传说》发售当时RPG主流的回合制战斗系统<ref name="YTtales">{{cite web|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cvbD7_pJOro|title=A History Of The Tales Series: The Road To Tales Of Xillia|author=[[PlayStation|PlayStation]] Access|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|date=2013-08-09|accessdate=2014-07-22|archive-date=2020-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041221/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cvbD7_pJOro|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

游戏中引入的一些特色公认人气很高，从而在之后的作品中沿用，“自由跑动”（角色在战场自由移动的能力）就是一例.<ref name="GamaAppeal">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/116063/CEDEC_09_Namcos_Tales_Studio_Aims_For_Many_Audiences.php|title=CEDEC 09: Namco's Tales Studio Aims For Many Audiences|author=Sato, Yoshi|publisher=Gamasutra|date=2009-09-03|accessdate=2014-07-22|archive-date=2020-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041229/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/116063/CEDEC_09_Namcos_Tales_Studio_Aims_For_Many_Audiences.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏轻度采用了回合制战斗元素：比如《宿命传说》和之后游戏采用的“连携容量”系统（角色可移发动多个技能）<ref name="IGNanniversary" /><ref name="GamaAppeal" />。《遗迹傳奇》的战斗系统特意设计的和乱斗类似：团队称这是希望将乱斗和传说游戏的故事与等级机制结合<ref name="Interview1">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2005/12/08/tales-of-legendia-interview?page=1 |title=Tales of Legendia Interview (Page 1) |publisher=IGN |date=2005-12-07 |accessdate=2013-06-07 |author=Adams, David |archive-date=2020-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712054852/https://www.ign.com/articles/2005/12/08/tales-of-legendia-interview?page=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。角色多可使用奥义，即战斗中的特殊攻击<ref name="ToX2preview">{{cite web|url=http://www.rpgsite.net/preview/3701-tales-of-xillia-2-hands-on|title=Tales of Xillia 2 Hands-On|author=Kreinberg, David|publisher=RPGSite|date=2014-06-30|accessdate=2014-07-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140719045553/http://rpgsite.net/preview/3701-tales-of-xillia-2-hands-on|archivedate=2014-07-19|deadurl=no}}</ref>。玩家一般只能控制单一角色<ref name="rpgfan.comGraces">{{cite web |url=http://rpgfan.com/reviews/Tales_of_Graces_F/index.html |title=RPGFan Reviews – Tales of Graces F |author=Liu, Abraham Ashton |publisher=RPGFan |date=2007-08-02 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-date=2019-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610040917/http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/Tales_of_Graces_F/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但《宿命传说》和以后的一些游戏有多人选项<ref name="1upInterview" /><ref name="IGNeternia">{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2001/07/13/tales-of-destiny-2-3|title=Tales of Destiny 2|author=IGN Staff|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2001-07-13|accessdate=2014-08-12}}</ref><ref name="RPGFphantasia">{{cite web|url=http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/talesofphantasia/Tales_of_Phantasia.html|title=Tales of Phantasia review|author=Soujirou, Seta|publisher=RPG Fan|accessdate=2014-08-12|archive-date=2020-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041357/http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/talesofphantasia/Tales_of_Phantasia.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

每作的战斗系统都有强化，并以特有的描述性名称表示：比如《圣恩传说》采用“风格切换”系统（角色可以在两类奥义中切换），《热情传说》采用“融合连锁”系统（人族角色和天族角色暂时合體並获得更强的戰鬥力）<ref name="RPGgraces">{{cite web|url=http://www.rpgamer.com/games/tales/tog/togprev.html|title=Tales of Graces F - Preview: Future Perfect|author=Fuller, Alex|publisher=RPGamer|accessdate=2014-07-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140520002332/http://www.rpgamer.com/games/tales/tog/togprev.html|archivedate=2014-05-20|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="IGNfestival" />。角色会获得“称号”，一些作品中给角色分配称号会赋予战斗加成<ref name="Joystiq review">{{cite web |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2012/03/16/tales-of-graces-f-review/ |title=''Tales of Graces f'' Joystiq review |first=Nathan |last=Grayson |date=2012-03-16 |publisher=Joystiq |accessdate=2012-05-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605224620/http://www.joystiq.com/2012/03/16/tales-of-graces-f-review/ |archivedate=2013-06-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。正篇中，在世界地图或环境中移动遇敌时，会切换到专门的画面展开战斗。而《热情传说》战斗会直接在地图画面中展开<ref name="GemBattleInfo">{{cite web|url=http://gematsu.com/2014/07/tales-zestiria-screenshots-show-matran-baltro-map-actions-real-map-battles|title=Tales of Zestiria screenshots show Matran, Baltro, map actions, real map battles, more|author=Romano, Sal|publisher=Gematsu|date=2014-07-24|accessdate=2014-07-24|archive-date=2015-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150922082747/http://gematsu.com/2014/07/tales-zestiria-screenshots-show-matran-baltro-map-actions-real-map-battles|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在大多传说游戏中，不同角色间会有戏剧和喜剧性的支线小品对话。这特色从《宿命传说》开始，而在英文版中大多被删去<ref name="TalesSkits">{{cite web|url=http://realotakugamer.com/namco-bandai-to-introduce-new-skit-system-to-tales-of-xillia|title=Namco Bandai To Introduce New Skit System To Tales of Xillia|author=Andreas, San|publisher=Real Otaku Gamer|date=2011-04-21|accessdate=2014-07-22|archive-date=2020-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041419/https://realotakugamer.com/namco-bandai-to-introduce-new-skit-system-to-tales-of-xillia|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ToDretro">{{cite web|url=http://gamerescape.com/game-review/classic-review-tales-of-destiny/|title=Classic Review: Tales of Destiny|publisher=Gamer Escape|date=2013-12-19|accessdate=2014-07-22|archive-date=2016-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330170015/http://gamerescape.com/game-review/classic-review-tales-of-destiny/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在英文GameCube版《仙乐传说》中，小品的配音被除去，但HD再版中收录了日版配音，因此也就保留了小品配音<ref name="KotakuToS">{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/four-reasons-to-be-excited-for-the-tales-of-symphonia-h-1460704058|title=Four Reasons to Be Excited for the Tales of Symphonia HD Remaster|author=Eisenbeis, Richard|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|date=2013-11-08|accessdate=2014-07-22|archive-date=2020-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041457/https://kotaku.com/four-reasons-to-be-excited-for-the-tales-of-symphonia-h-1460704058|dead-url=no}}</ref>。首个英文版小品全配音的作品是《薄暮传说》；也有《深渊传说》配音的计划，但因容量问题砍去<ref name="1upInterview">{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/previews/tales-of-vesperia_3|title=Tales of Vesperia Preview|author=1UP Staff|publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|date=2008-04-16|accessdate=2014-05-31|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106014335/http://www.1up.com/previews/tales-of-vesperia_3|archivedate=2012-11-06|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。料理系统也是常见的系统，这些游戏中角色可以制作料理回复体力，料理制作也有类似经验值的系统<ref name="ToVreview">{{cite web|url=http://www.rpgamer.com/games/tales/tov/reviews/tovstrev2.html|title=Tales of Vesperia - Staff Review: A Familiar Aer About it|author=Motok, Oliver|publisher=RPGamer|accessdate=2014-07-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110309040509/http://www.rpgamer.com/games/tales/tov/reviews/tovstrev2.html|archivedate=2011-03-09|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

=== 主题、情节与角色 ===

传说系列著名的叙事主题是不同种族间的共存问题<ref name="IGNorigins">{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2014/06/26/why-90-of-fans-at-tales-of-festival-are-female|title=Why 90% of Fans at Tales of Festival Are Female|author=Robson, Daniel|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2014-06-26|accessdate=2014-07-15|archive-date=2014-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701003126/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/06/26/why-90-of-fans-at-tales-of-festival-are-female|dead-url=no}}</ref>。典例是大量探索种族主义主题的《重生传说》，编剧平松正树的灵感来自[[南斯拉夫|南斯拉夫]]的种族冲突<ref>{{cite book |script-title=ja:テイルズ オブ リバース 公式コンプリートガイド|date=2005-01-31 |language=ja |isbn=978-4-902372-05-2|page=466|publisher=Namco Bandai Books}}</ref>。根植围绕争议于信仰等主题的剧情角色是另一常见性质<ref name="ToZopenworld">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2013/12/24/tales-games-like-moving-highway-tales-zestiria-wont-like/|title=Tales Games Are Like Moving On A Highway, Tales Of Zestiria Won't Be Like That|author=Spencer|publisher=Siliconera|date=2013-12-24|accessdate=2014-04-09|archive-date=2015-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150113032503/http://www.siliconera.com/2013/12/24/tales-games-like-moving-highway-tales-zestiria-wont-like/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。系列各作主题由系列制作人根据当前世界事件决定<ref name="RPGbabainterview">{{cite web|url=http://www.rpgsite.net/interview/3159-talking-tales-with-hideo-baba-tales-of-series-producer|title=Talking Tales with Hideo Baba, Tales of Series Producer|author=Chun, Simon|publisher=RPG Site|date=2013-10-11|accessdate=2014-08-02|archive-date=2020-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041436/https://www.rpgsite.net/interview/3159-talking-tales-with-hideo-baba-tales-of-series-producer|dead-url=no}}</ref>。主题选择有助于指示游戏的名称：一旦主题确定，团队就会搜索各种语言寻找合适的代表词<ref name="BabaJPinterviewA">{{cite web|url=http://jpgames.de/2013/11/manga-games-show-2013-unser-interview-mit-hideo-baba/|title=Tales of: Unser Interview mit Producer Hideo Baba|trans_title=Tales of: Our Interview with Producer Hideo Baba|author=Robertastic|publisher=JPGames.de|date=2013-11-04|accessdate=2014-08-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131108195200/http://jpgames.de/2013/11/manga-games-show-2013-unser-interview-mit-hideo-baba/|archivedate=2013-11-08|deadurl=no}}</ref>。在2008年制作者访谈中，[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]称各故事叙事“非常同质”，但受访者表示此观点源自这样一种事实：西方爱好者多未无日本文化阅历，因此看起来每作间非常相似。每部游戏都聘请各自项目的编剧，包括自由职业者和内部编剧。实弥岛巧是参与多个项目的编剧之一，编写了《仙乐传说》和《深渊传说》的故事<ref name="GamaInterview" />。故事主要设定在高度幻想的世界，制作人不选择阴暗或者科幻的设定<ref name="PSBlogBaba">{{cite web|url=http://blog.eu.playstation.com/2014/08/14/hideo-baba-answers-tales-xillia-questions/|title=Hideo Baba answers your Tales of Xillia questions|author=Ferdjani, Isshak|publisher=[[PlayStation|PlayStation]] Blog|date=2014-08-14|accessdate=2014-08-20|archive-date=2014-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821085744/http://blog.eu.playstation.com/2014/08/14/hideo-baba-answers-tales-xillia-questions/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。采用现代设定，比一般作品跟阴暗的《无尽传说2》例外。确认称该方向为系列的一次性实验<ref name="RPGbabainterview" />。

在传说游戏中主角扮演关键角色，不完全原因是各做中都需要他们来描述主题<ref name="RPGbabainterview" />。《深渊传说》尝试冒险最开始不讨喜的异端主人公<ref name="TalesGenres" />。团队为了提升目标群年龄限制，在《薄暮传说》中采用更成熟的主人公<ref name="GamaInterview" />。《無盡传说》除了男主人公裘德·马西斯外，还初次采用女主人公[[米拉·麦克斯韦|米拉·麦克斯韦]]，虽然当时称没有创作单女主人公游戏的坚实计划<ref name="GemBaba">{{cite web|url=http://gematsu.com/2012/10/interview-tales-producer-hideo-baba-on-tales-of-xillia-more|title=Interview: Tales producer Hideo Baba on Tales of Xillia, more|author=Romano, Sal|publisher=Gematsu|date=2012-10-16|accessdate=2014-08-04|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111145932/https://www.gematsu.com/2012/10/interview-tales-producer-hideo-baba-on-tales-of-xillia-more|dead-url=no}}</ref>。让玩家在角色上看到自己的影子是另一高优先考虑<ref name="SpongBaba" />。

=== 专用语 ===

系列中会用独特的专用语指代游戏。2007年吉積宣布将传说游戏分类“旗艦作品”和“护航舰作品”两类<ref name="touch-ds1">{{cite web|url=http://touch-ds.jp/crv/vol7/005.html|title=Creator's Voice|publisher=Nintendo DS Creator's Voice|accessdate=2014-07-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071124153348/http://touch-ds.jp/crv/vol7/005.html|archivedate=2007-11-24|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。“旗艦”概念上為“正統新作”，“护航舰”则对应“衍生作品”。两类游戏的内部差别是，“护航舰作品”不为旗艦游戏提供灵感，而是借鉴它们最受欢迎的元素<ref name="IGNorigins" />。游戏多有“特有種類名稱”，基本为概括游戏总主题的解释性标题或短语，如《永恒传说》的是“永遠和羈絆的RPG”。据吉积称主要原因是，不应将传说系列当做开发团队创作的角色扮演系列，而应是“角色的扮演游戏”——玩家不将游戏角色当做化身，而是了解并看着他们成长：种类名表示将他们与其他角色扮演游戏相区别<ref name="TalesGenres">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2011/06/23/tales-games-arent-rpgs-says-tales-of-the-abyss-producer/|title=Tales Games Aren't RPGs, Says Tales of the Abyss Producer|author=Laura|publisher=Siliconera|date=2011-06-23|accessdate=2014-07-22|archive-date=2016-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161121185747/http://www.siliconera.com/2011/06/23/tales-games-arent-rpgs-says-tales-of-the-abyss-producer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而这些术语在英语本地化版中大量除去。重制或移植版也有专用语：“R”代表“重制”（{{lang|en|remake}}）或“重新想象”（{{lang|en|re-imagination}}，出现于《心灵传说R》），而《圣恩传说f》中的“F”表示“未来”（{{lang|en|future}}），指代游戏增加的故事内容<ref name="KotakuNamco4">{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/tales-rpgs-are-like-gumdrops-says-the-guy-who-makes-th-470869380|title=Tales RPGs Are Like Gumdrops, Says The Guy Who Makes Them|author=Shreier, Jason|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|date=2013-04-05|accessdate=2014-08-02|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119003557/https://kotaku.com/tales-rpgs-are-like-gumdrops-says-the-guy-who-makes-th-470869380|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="HeartsRtease1">{{cite web|url=http://gematsu.com/2012/01/tales-of-innocence-r-credits-tease-another-tales-remake|title=Tales of Innocence R credits tease another Tales remake|author=Romano, Sal|publisher=Gematsu|date=2012-01-25|accessdate=2014-08-11|archive-date=2014-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812204503/http://gematsu.com/2012/01/tales-of-innocence-r-credits-tease-another-tales-remake|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="SilGraces">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2010/08/02/tales-of-graces-f-includes-a-tale-about-asbels-future/|title=Tales Of Graces F Includes A Tale About Asbel's Future|author=Spencer|publisher=Siliconera|date=2010-08-02|accessdate=2014-08-02|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629194957/https://www.siliconera.com/2010/08/02/tales-of-graces-f-includes-a-tale-about-asbels-future/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 开发 ==

=== 历史 ===

系列初代游戏《幻想传说》改编自游戏编剧兼主程序员五反田义治的未出版小说《幻想-{}-传说》（{{lang|en|''Tale Phantasia''}}）。在编写游戏故事中，遗弃或改编了几个原小说元素<ref>{{cite book |work=Tales of Chronicle: Tales of Series 15th Kinen Official Settei Shiryoushu |date=2011-03-14 |language=ja |isbn=4-902372-34-7 |page=190 |publisher=Namco Bandai Games}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |work=Tales of Chronicle: Tales of Series 15th Kinen Official Settei Shiryoushu |date=2011-03-14 |language=ja |isbn=4-902372-34-7 |page=253 |publisher=Namco Bandai Games}}</ref>。游戏1986年建立的独立游戏开发工作室由[[狼组|狼组]]开发<ref name="GRhistory" />。因原雇主[[日本通讯网络|日本通讯网络]]能力糟糕，多名狼组成员寻求独立的游戏发行商。在和[[艾尼克斯|艾尼克斯]]协定未果后，他们和南梦宫（现万代南梦宫）签订了发行合同<ref name="LevelInterview">{{cite journal | last1= Villner | first1=Pär | last2= Schaufelberger| first2=Fredrik |date=September 2009 | title=Square Enix | journal=Level | issue=29 | pages=44–59|language=sv | publisher= | location=Sweaden}}</ref>。超级任天堂版《幻想传说》开发周期陷入困境，狼组和南梦宫就许多创意产生分歧<ref name="rpgamer">{{cite web |url=http://www.rpgamer.com/games/tales/top/reviews/topgbastrev2.html |title=> Staff Retroview > Tales of Phantasia |publisher=RPGamer |date= |accessdate=2012-08-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140414083857/http://www.rpgamer.com/games/tales/top/reviews/topgbastrev2.html |archivedate=2014-04-14 }}</ref>。分歧导致大部分狼组成员在游戏开发后离开建立新公司[[tri-Ace|tri-Ace]]，即[[星之海洋系列|星之海洋系列]]的开发商<ref name="rpgamer" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nintendolife.com/reviews/2009/04/star_ocean_retro |title=Star Ocean (Super Nintendo) Review |publisher=Nintendo Life |date=2009-04-09 |accessdate=2012-08-18 |archive-date=2012-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120820103640/http://www.nintendolife.com/reviews/2009/04/star_ocean_retro |dead-url=no }}</ref>。留下来的成员继续开发传说系列游戏<ref name="rpgamer" />。

工作室一直独立，直到2003年被万代南梦宫吸收后易名南梦宫万代工作室<ref name="GRhistory">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/tales-studio-shut-down-namco-bandai/|title=Tales Studio shut down by Namco Bandai|author=Goulter, Tom|publisher=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]|date=2011-11-21|accessdate=2014-08-02|archive-date=2020-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041519/https://www.gamesradar.com/tales-studio-shut-down-namco-bandai/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。万代南梦宫、日本通讯网络和系列总监[[菊池荣二|菊池荣二]]分别持有工作室的股份。2006年南梦宫买下了通讯网络的股份，再之后又买下了菊池的，从而完全控制工作室<ref name="GSnamcotales">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/namco-creates-subsidiary-for-tales-series/1100-6024237/|title=Namco creates subsidiary for Tales series|author=Niizumi, Hirohiko|publisher=[[Gamespot|Gamespot]]|date=2003-03-31|accessdate=2014-08-13|archive-date=2020-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041511/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/namco-creates-subsidiary-for-tales-series/1100-6024237/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="EdgeShares">{{cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/news/namco-bandai-absorb-and-close-tales-studio/#null|title=Namco Bandai to absorb and close Tales studio|author=Brown, Nathan|publisher=[[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]]|date=2011-11-21|accessdate=2014-08-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130531064345/http://www.edge-online.com/news/namco-bandai-absorb-and-close-tales-studio/#null|archivedate=2013-05-31|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2011年中段的财政报告显示南梦宫传说出于严重财政困难，有2011万美元债务，同时报告上一财年亏损<ref name="KotakuNamco1">{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5568531/end-of-story-for-tails-studio|title=Tales Studio Is Not Doing So Well|author=Ashcraft, Brian|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|date=2011-06-21|accessdate=2014-07-22|archive-date=2018-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181115150627/https://kotaku.com/5568531/end-of-story-for-tails-studio|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年11月母公司正式宣布吸收工作室<ref name="KotakuNamco2">{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5568531/end-of-story-for-tails-studio|title=Was This Inevitable? The Tales Studio Is Dead|author=Eisenbeis, Richard|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|date=2011-11-21|accessdate=2014-08-02|archive-date=2018-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181115150627/https://kotaku.com/5568531/end-of-story-for-tails-studio|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在南梦宫传说被吸收后，原系列品牌管理人[[马场英雄|马场英雄]]被指定担任系列制作人。他曾担任过原版《心灵传说》制作人<ref name="KotakuNamco3">{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5944485/tales-studio-getting-absorbed-by-namco-bandai-wasnt-such-a-bad-thing-after-all|title=Tales Studio Getting Absorbed By Namco Bandai Wasn't Such A Bad Thing After All|author=Nakamura, Toshi|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|date=2012-09-19|accessdate=2014-08-02|archive-date=2018-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181103103012/https://kotaku.com/5944485/tales-studio-getting-absorbed-by-namco-bandai-wasnt-such-a-bad-thing-after-all|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BabaHearts">{{cite web|url=http://www.famitsu.com/interview/article/1216801_1493.html|publisher=[[Famitsu|Famitsu]]|author=Famitsu|title=『テイルズ オブハーツ』プロデューサー馬場氏と白組・小池氏にインタビュー|date=2008-07-18|accessdate=2008-09-29|archive-date=2013-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130214074741/http://www.famitsu.com/interview/article/1216801_1493.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同时吉积信担任总系列制作人，他参与过《宿命传说》和《圣洁传说》等多部游戏的制作<ref name="TalesFamitsuYoshizumi" /><ref name="KotakuNamco1" /><ref name="NamcoYoshizumi">{{cite web|url=http://www.bandainamcogames.com/company/news.html?news_id=20&page=8|title=Press Release - NAMCO BANDAI GAMES AMERICA INC. ANNOUNCES TALES OF ZESTIRIA FOR THE PLAYSTATON 3 SYSTEM|author=|publisher=[[Bandai_Namco_Games|Bandai Namco Games]]|date=2013-12-12|accessdate=2014-08-13|archive-date=2014-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019103348/http://www.bandainamcogames.com/company/news.html?news_id=20&page=8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 艺术设计 ===

系列采用模仿竞争[[日本动漫|动漫]]的卓越艺术风格<ref name="YTtales" />。马场称，当制作团队决定主角的故事、个性和环境后才创作角色设计。此外画师可以用自己的想象，但也会被要求修改着装细节和面部表情<ref name="GemBabaDesigns">{{cite web|url=http://gematsu.com/2012/05/tales-fans-interview-series-producer-part-2|title=Tales fans interview series producer – part 2|author=Romano, Sal|publisher=Gematsu|date=2012-05-02|accessdate=2014-08-18|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112021302/https://www.gematsu.com/2012/05/tales-fans-interview-series-producer-part-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。漫画家[[藤岛康介|藤岛康介]]是系列主设计师之一。他从《幻想传说》就开始参与角色设计，此后他还为《深渊传说》、《薄暮传说》和《无尽传说》等作品设计角色<ref name="YTtales" /><ref name="Playtest">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/08/04/tales-of-phantasia-playtest-2 |title=Tales of Phantasia Playtest |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |accessdate=2013-07-06 |date=2003-08-04 |author=Gantayat, Anoop |archive-date=2013-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131010234018/http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/08/04/tales-of-phantasia-playtest-2 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Tales of the Abyss Trailer |date=2005-08-25 |accessdate=2013-06-11 |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |author=Gantayat, Anoop |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2005/08/25/tales-of-the-abyss-trailer |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041522/https://www.ign.com/articles/2005/08/25/tales-of-the-abyss-trailer |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一名设计师[[猪股睦美|猪股睦美]]从《宿命传说》参与设计，他参与了《永恒传说》、《重生传说》和《无尽传说》等设计<ref name="YTtales" /><ref name="SilInomata">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2013/05/18/saga-final-fantasy-and-tales-artists-create-shin-megami-tensei-iv-artwork/|title=SaGa, Final Fantasy, And Tales Artists Create Shin Megami Tensei IV Artwork|author=Spencer|publisher=Siliconera|date=2013-05-18|accessdate=2014-07-23|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629103056/https://www.siliconera.com/2013/05/18/saga-final-fantasy-and-tales-artists-create-shin-megami-tensei-iv-artwork/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第三名长期设计师是[[奥村大悟|奥村大悟]]，他为《无尽传说2》和《交響曲傳奇 拉塔特斯克的騎士》设计角色<ref name="SilOkumura">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2013/10/17/tales-xillia-2-character-designer-designing-world-characters/|title=How Namco Bandai Is Making More Realistic Characters For Tales of Xillia 2|author=Kris|publisher=Siliconera|date=2013-10-17|accessdate=2014-07-22|archive-date=2019-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190218082130/https://www.siliconera.com/2013/10/17/tales-xillia-2-character-designer-designing-world-characters/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他设计师还有[[中澤一登|中澤一登]]（《遗迹传说》）<ref name="IGN1">{{cite web |title=Kill Bill Anime Director to Work on Tales Game |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2005/02/18/kill-bill-anime-director-to-work-on-tales-game |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |author=Gantayat, Anoop |date=2005-02-18 |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2020-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713052845/https://www.ign.com/articles/2005/02/18/kill-bill-anime-director-to-work-on-tales-game |dead-url=no }}</ref>、木村浩一（《无尽传说2》）和岩本稔（《热情传说》）<ref name="USpreview">{{cite web|url=http://www.usgamer.net/articles/tgs-tales-of-reinvigorated-localization|title=TGS: Tales of Reinvigorated Localization|author=Parish, Jeremy|publisher=USGamer|date=2013-09-19|accessdate=2014-06-23|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929183529/https://www.usgamer.net/articles/tgs-tales-of-reinvigorated-localization|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Localizations">{{cite web| url=http://gematsu.com/2013/12/tales-of-zestiria-confirmed-for-worldwide-release| title=Tales of Zestiria confirmed for worldwide release| first=Sal| last=Romano| date=2013-12-12| publisher=Gematsu| accessdate=2013-12-13| archive-date=2015-09-18| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918220904/http://gematsu.com/2013/12/tales-of-zestiria-confirmed-for-worldwide-release| dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏世界和角色的艺术设计风格从卡通渲染动画（《薄暮传说》）到写实风格（《无尽传说2》）不一<ref name="1upInterview" /><ref name="USpreview" />。作品的艺术风格由开发者依主题和故事决定<ref name="SpongBaba" />。

游戏有动画过场，同时制作团队为提升玩家第一印象而将之视为重点。系列力避一般动漫的夸张等修饰、以及作品间的常见叙事元素<ref name="GamaHistory">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/179710/How_Namco_keeps_its_Tales_Of_RPG_series_fresh_17_years_later.php|title=How Namco keeps its Tales Of RPG series fresh, 17 years later|author=Sheffield, Brandon|publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|date=2012-11-02|accessdate=2014-07-22|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013113/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/179710/How_Namco_keeps_its_Tales_Of_RPG_series_fresh_17_years_later.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《宿命传说》是首部采用这种过场动画的作品<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/tekken-3-release-date-confirmed-2462586 |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |author=Chris Johnston and Joe Fielder |date=1998-02-02 |title=Tekken 3 Release Date Confirmed |accessdate=2013-07-02 |archive-date=2013-07-03 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130703031613/http://www.gamespot.com/news/tekken-3-release-date-confirmed-2462586 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。除了《无尽传说》和《无尽传说2》外的过场由[[Production_I.G|Production I.G]]制作；为了展示系列的新艺术方向，这款游戏的动画交由[[Ufotable|Ufotable]]制作<ref name="SpongBaba">{{cite web|url=http://spong.com/feature/10110568/Interview-Tales-of-Reminiscence-RPG-Producer-Hideo-Baba|title=Interviews// Tales of Reminiscence: RPG Producer Hideo Baba|author=Joscelyne, Svend|publisher=Spong.com|date=2011-12-16|accessdate=2014-07-23|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027053832/https://spong.com/feature/10110568/Interview-Tales-of-Reminiscence-RPG-Producer-Hideo-Baba|dead-url=no}}</ref>。制作团队作为实验，发行了两种任天堂DS《心灵传说》版本，其一采用Production I.G的传统动画，其二采用Shirogumi公司的[[计算机成像|计算机成像]]（CGI）过场。结果显示在爱好者群中CGI过场比动画过场冷门<ref name="FamTheme">{{cite web|url=http://www.famitsu.com/game/coming/1216522_1407.html|title=人の心が通じ合う出会いの旅に出よう 『テイルズ オブ ハーツ』|publisher=[[Famitsu|Famitsu]]|date=2008-07-14|accessdate=2014-08-11|archive-date=2014-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812203745/http://www.famitsu.com/game/coming/1216522_1407.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="JPGbabainterviewC">{{cite web|url=http://jpgames.de/2013/05/our-interview-with-tales-of-producer-hideo-baba-2/|title=Our interview with Tales of-Producer Hideo Baba|author=Tony|publisher=JPGames.net|date=2013-05-26|accessdate=2014-08-11|archive-date=2014-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808155256/http://jpgames.de/2013/05/our-interview-with-tales-of-producer-hideo-baba-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 技术与开发团队 ===

游戏引擎通常由内部开发：列举的理由包括外包开发的问题。在《薄暮传说》前，开发以项目为基础进行，为每部作品制作新开发工具和引擎。因为支出增长，开发过程改编，并朝使用更易用引擎方向简化<ref name="GamaInterview" />。工作室分为两支团队，宿命团队开发《宿命传说》等2D作品，仙乐团队开发3D作品<ref name="GamaInterview">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=19327|title=Interview: Xbox 360's Japanese Saviors Talk Tales Series|author=Nutt, Christian|publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|date=2008-08-26|accessdate=2014-05-31|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131112174236/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=19327|archivedate=2013-11-12|deadurl=no}}</ref>。在公司内部，除了一些核心人员，两个工作室有分别重大<ref name="GamaInterview" />。在2011年南梦宫传说被合并前，大部分主要传说游戏都由他们制作<ref name="KotakuNamco2" />。由万代南梦宫内部开发的《遗迹传说》和[[Alfa_System|Alfa System]]开发的《純真傳奇》是兩個重要例外<ref name="rpgfan_a">{{cite web |url=http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/talesoflegendia/index.html |title=RPGFan Reviews – Tales of Legendia |publisher=Rpgfan.com |date= |accessdate=2012-08-19 |archive-date=2019-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610135438/http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/talesoflegendia/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Interview2">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2005/12/08/tales-of-legendia-interview?page=2 |title=Tales of Legendia Interview (Page 2) |publisher=IGN |date=2005-12-07 |accessdate=2013-06-07 |author=Adams, David |archive-date=2020-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713145223/https://www.ign.com/articles/2005/12/08/tales-of-legendia-interview?page=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="bare_url" />。Alfa System還開發了許多掌上機衍生作品<ref name="GamaInterview" />。在南夢宮傳奇被萬代南夢宮合併後，原團隊和職員在成立新內部開發工作室萬代南夢宮工作室時重組<ref name="GemBabaStaff">{{cite web|url=http://gematsu.com/2012/05/famitsu-no-1224-tales-series-producer-interiew|title=Famitsu No. 1224: Tales Series Producer Interview|author=Slayton, Olivia|publisher=Gematsu|date=2011-05-18|accessdate=2014-08-18|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111233642/https://www.gematsu.com/2012/05/famitsu-no-1224-tales-series-producer-interiew|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 音樂 ===

傳奇系列主要作曲人是[[櫻庭統|櫻庭統]]。他早在《幻想传说》就参与作曲，此后作为自由作曲家的他为几乎全部正篇谱曲<ref name="SakurabaInterview">{{cite web|url=http://www.vgmonline.net/motoisakurabainterview/|title=Motoi Sakuraba Interview: Diverse New Projects|publisher=Game Music Online|date=2011-12-15|accessdate=2014-08-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140421223355/http://www.vgmonline.net/motoisakurabainterview/|archivedate=2014-04-21|deadurl=no}}</ref>。樱庭统标志的乐风在他大多数传说配乐上体现<ref name="RPGxillia">{{cite web|url=http://www.rpgfan.com/soundtracks/toxostse/index.html|title=Review - Tales of Xillia OST|author=Heemsbergen, Derek|publisher=RPGFan|date=2011-09-07|accessdate=2014-08-04|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603224119/http://www.rpgfan.com/soundtracks/toxostse/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他还频繁和作曲家田村信二合作<ref name="SakurabaInterview" />。在樱庭统未参与的游戏中，《遗迹传说》由内部作曲家[[椎名豪|椎名豪]]作曲<ref name="ShiinaInterview">{{cite web|url=http://www.vgmonline.net/goshiinainterview/|title=Go Shiina Interview: A Magical Mystery Tour|publisher=Game Music Online|date=2009-11-15|accessdate=2014-08-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140804195933/http://www.vgmonline.net/goshiinainterview/|archivedate=2014-08-04|deadurl=no}}</ref>，《純真傳奇》由中村和宏配乐<ref name="ANNinnocence">{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.co.uk/interest/2011-12-11/tales-of-innocence-r-rpg-3rd-promo-video-streamed|title=Tales of Innocence R RPG's 3rd Promo Video Streamed|author=Loo, Egan|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=2011-12-11|accessdate=2014-08-04}}{{Dead link|date=2019年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。樱庭和椎名合作为《热情传说》配乐<ref name="BabaJPinterviewB">{{cite web|url=http://jpgames.de/2014/08/animagic-2014-our-interview-with-hideo-baba/|title=AnimagiC 2014: Our interview with Hideo Baba|author=Tony|publisher=JPGames.de|date=2014-08-03|accessdate=2014-08-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140804110436/http://jpgames.de/2014/08/animagic-2014-our-interview-with-hideo-baba/|archivedate=2014-08-04|deadurl=no}}</ref>。系列许多游戏的主题曲采用不同日本歌手的授权歌曲，歌手包括[[GARNET_CROW|Garent Crow]]（《永恒传说》）、[[DEEN|Deen]]（《遗迹传说》、《心灵传说》）、[[KOKIA|Kokia]]（《純真傳奇》）、[[滨崎步|滨崎步]]（《无尽传说》、《无尽传说2》）等<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/cs/list/talesofeternia/song01.html |publisher=Bandai Namco |accessdate=2013-06-28 |script-title=ja:テイルズ オブ エターニア / バンダイナムコゲームス公式サイト |trans_title=Tales of Eternia / Bandai Namco Games Official Site |language=ja |archive-date=2013-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510163238/http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/cs/list/talesofeternia/song01.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="FamDEEN">{{cite web|url=http://www.famitsu.com/game/news/1218243_1124.html|title=DEENのライブにファンも総立ち！ "テイルズ オブ フェスティバル 2008"が開催|publisher=[[Famitsu|Famitsu]]|date=2008-09-23|accessdate=2014-08-11|archive-date=2014-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812210645/http://www.famitsu.com/game/news/1218243_1124.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2012-06-02/tales-of-xillia-2-brings-back-ayumi-hamasaki-ufotable|title=Tales of Xillia 2 Brings Back Ayumi Hamasaki, ufotable (Updated)|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=2012-06-02|accessdate=2014-08-07|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021103001/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2012-06-02/tales-of-xillia-2-brings-back-ayumi-hamasaki-ufotable|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=KOKIA｜NDS用ソフト"テイルズ オブ イノセンス" オープニングテーマ 「Follow the Nightingale」｜@Victor Entertainment | url=http://www.jvcmusic.co.jp/-/Discography/A012051/VTCL-35011.html | publisher=[[Victor_Entertainment|Victor Entertainment]] | language=ja | accessdate=2010-05-02 | archive-date=2009-09-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090928071759/http://www.jvcmusic.co.jp/-/Discography/A012051/VTCL-35011.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。许多早期游戏英文化版删去了主题曲，比如《仙乐传说》用管弦乐版替换了主题歌<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/04/30/pre-e3-2004-tales-of-symphonia-interview?page=2 |title=Pre-E3 2004: Tales of Symphonia Interview Page 2 |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2004-04-30 |accessdate=2012-05-13 |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041730/https://www.ign.com/articles/2004/04/30/pre-e3-2004-tales-of-symphonia-interview?page=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/06/18/tales-of-symphonia-faq?page=4 |title=Tales of Symphonia FAQ Page 4 |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2004-06-11 |accessdate=2012-05-13 |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041736/https://www.ign.com/articles/2004/06/18/tales-of-symphonia-faq?page=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最早采用日版主题曲的西方版传说作品是《薄暮传说》<ref name="VesperiaTheme">{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2008/04/17/tales-of-vesperia-goes-pink|title=Tales Of Vesperia Goes Pink|author=IGN Music|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2008-05-17|accessdate=2014-05-31|archive-date=2014-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220052426/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/04/17/tales-of-vesperia-goes-pink|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 本地化 ===

傳奇系列游戏只有PlayStation 2版《宿命传说2》有官方中文版。马场在2012年的采访中表示“目前尚无任何‘亚洲在地化’的计划”<ref name="gnn">{{Cite web |url=http://gnn.gamer.com.tw/6/73226.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-01-13 |archive-date=2014-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111123023/http://gnn.gamer.com.tw/6/73226.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

多部传说作品，特别是大多衍生作品，没有在西方本地化或仅在北美發行：前者如正篇中的《重生传说》和《純真傳奇》，後者如《遗迹传说》<ref name="JoyLocalRebirth" /><ref name="InnocenceLocal" /><ref name="EuroEurope">{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/news210606tales|title=Four new Tales RPGs|author=Bramwell, Tom|publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2006-06-21|accessdate=2014-08-03|archive-date=2020-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041754/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/news210606tales|dead-url=no}}</ref>。马场在2013年表示，正篇比衍生作品本地化优先度高。此外他还称，本体化团队有限，他们需要“挑选”在西方发行什么游戏<ref name="SilLocalInterview">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2013/10/25/tales-team-simply-doesnt-enough-staff-localize-every-game/|title=The Tales Team Simply Doesn't Have Enough Staff To Localize Every Game|author=Kai, Cheng|publisher=Siliconera|date=2013-10-25|accessdate=2014-06-23|archive-date=2019-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616055722/https://www.siliconera.com/2013/10/25/tales-team-simply-doesnt-enough-staff-localize-every-game/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。西方版《永恒传说》名为“宿命传说2”，原因是潜在的商标冲突和充分利用《永恒传说》的知名度<ref name="ToD2interview" />。万代南梦宫计划《热情传说》的西方版和日版同年发行<ref name="ZestYears">{{cite web|url=http://gematsu.com/2014/06/tales-zestiria-will-hit-west-year-hits-japan|title=Tales of Zestiria will hit the west the same year it hits Japan|author=Romano, Sal|publisher=Gematsu|date=2014-06-18|accessdate=2014-06-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140618210054/http://gematsu.com/2014/06/tales-zestiria-will-hit-west-year-hits-japan|archivedate=2014-06-18|deadurl=no}}</ref>。做出此决定乃因《无尽传说》和续作的推延发行，以及西方爱好者对此的反应<ref name= "IGNfestival">{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2014/06/26/tales-of-zestiriaas-secret-weapon-is-fusionic-chain|title=Tales of Zestiria's Secret Weapon is Fusionic Chain|author=Robson, Daniel|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2014-06-26|accessdate=2014-07-15|archive-date=2014-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140628223643/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/06/26/tales-of-zestiriaas-secret-weapon-is-fusionic-chain|dead-url=no}}</ref>。爱好者亦有民间翻译，如原版《幻想传说》和《純真傳奇》<ref name="bare_url">{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2006/02/22/tales-of-phantasia-2 |title=Tales of Phantasia – Game Boy Advance Preview at IGN |author=Bozon, Mark |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2006-02-21 |accessdate=2012-08-18}}</ref><ref name="InnocenceLocal" />。虽然爱好者强烈要求西方版加入日本配音，但授权问题多制约了万代南梦宫<ref name="RPGbabainterview" />。手机游戏因是和日本专用手机开发商合作，其本地化也被置于低优先度<ref name="BabaJPinterviewA" />。

=== 译名 ===

傳奇系列正編第一作《幻想传说》（{{lang|en|''Tales of Phantasia''}}）由於劇情含有[[時間旅行|時間旅行]]，因此在台灣發售時，被譯作“時空-{}-幻境”，而在第二作《宿命传说》（{{lang|en|''Tales of Destiny''}}）發行後，劇情雖無時光旅行，但被當做系列作，譯成“時空-{}-幻境2”，而在第三作《永恒传说》（{{lang|en|''Tales of Eternia''}}）發售後，台灣對此作則有“時空-{}-幻境3”與“永恆傳奇”兩種不同的稱呼，但基本上仍以稱呼“時空-{}-幻境3”的人佔多數，到了系列第四作《宿命传说2》（{{lang|en|''Tales of Destiny 2''}}）發售後，由於劇情延續於《宿命传说》，無法再被譯作“時空-{}-幻境4”，故隨原始名稱譯作“命運傳奇2”，此後發售的正編系列作亦是對原始名稱進行中譯，不再有“時空-{}-幻境”的譯名，而在這之前發售第二、三作也開始被人稱做“命運-{}-傳奇”、“永恆-{}-傳奇”；“時空-{}-幻境2”、“時空-{}-幻境3”變成只是少數人的稱呼，至於第一作的中文譯名仍以“時空-{}-幻境”為主流稱呼，也有称呼“时空幻境 幻想传奇”的，但並未隨原始名稱改稱做“幻想-{}-傳奇”<ref name="gnn" />。

== 评价与影响 ==

系列自诞生以来一般都销量良好。系列销售主力在日本：2007年时销量87%在日本、8%在北美、3%在欧洲、2%在中国大陆。当时最畅销的作品是《仙乐传说》（GameCube版95.3万，PlayStation 2版48.6万），《宿命传说》（PlayStation版110万），《无尽传说》（PlayStation 3版100万）和《宿命传说2》（PlayStation 2版97.7万）；该销量不计手机游戏和在线游戏<ref name="RPGFsales">{{cite web |title=Tales Series Sales Top 10 Million Mark |author=Winkler, Chris |publisher=RPGFan |date=2007-12-11 |url=http://www.rpgfan.com/news/2007/1398.html |accessdate=2009-08-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517153604/http://www.rpgfan.com/news/2007/1398.html |archivedate=2014-05-17 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="SilTotalSales" />。系列的成功还促进了对应游戏机的销售：《薄暮传说》登陆Xbox 360让该主机在日本首次卖完，同样因为对于目标受众，次世代主机销售前景渺茫，南梦宫决定为PlayStation 3开发《热情传说》<ref name="IGNorigins" /><ref>{{cite web |last=Ransom |first=James |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2008/08/20/xbox-360-sold-out-in-japan/ |title=Xbox 360 sold out in Japan |publisher=Joystiq.com |date=2008-08-20 |accessdate=2013-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018021816/http://www.joystiq.com/2008/08/20/xbox-360-sold-out-in-japan/ |archive-date=2012-10-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。到2013年12月时，系列已经在全球100个地区出货1600万套<ref name="SilTotalSales">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2013/12/13/altogether-namco-bandai-shipped-16-million-tales-games/|title=Altogether, Namco Bandai Shipped Over 16 Million Tales Games|author=Spencer|publisher=Siliconera|date=2013-12-13|accessdate=2014-08-01|archive-date=2019-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616061823/https://www.siliconera.com/2013/12/13/altogether-namco-bandai-shipped-16-million-tales-games/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

虽然传说系列在英文区一直难受瞩目，但在日本被视为最庞大的角色扮演游戏系列之一。[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]的杰里米·帕里什在2001年称，传说系列在日本仅次于[[最终幻想|最终幻想]]和[[勇者斗恶龙|勇者斗恶龙]]，是第三大RPG系列<ref>{{cite web |last=Parish |first=Jeremy |url=http://www.1up.com/previews/tales-tempest_2 |title=Tales of the Tempest Preview for DS from |publisher=1UP.com |date=2006-09-22 |accessdate=2012-08-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130516155326/http://www.1up.com/previews/tales-tempest_2 |archivedate=2013-05-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]布兰登·谢菲尔德同样称，“虽然系列没有最终幻想在西方或勇者斗恶龙在日本那样的文化蕴藏，但仍然是全球非常流行的品牌”<ref name="GamaHistory" />。[[IGN|IGN]]的Anoop Gantayat称就销量而言，传说是第三大日式角色扮演游戏系列<ref>{{cite web|last=Gantayat|first=Anoop|title=Tales Headed For Big Sales|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2004/12/16/tales-headed-for-big-sales|publisher=IGN|date=2004-12-15|accessdate=2014-08-01}}</ref>。系列《宿命传说》和《遗迹传说》等作品可以和[[街头霸王|街头霸王]]等格斗或乱斗游戏比肩<ref name="YTtales" /><ref name="rpgfan.comGraces" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rpgamer.com/games/tales/tod/reviews/todrdrev3.html |title=Tales of Destiny – Review |publisher=Rpgamer.com |date= |accessdate=2013-07-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Cz1tWdMu?url=http://www.rpgamer.com/games/tales/tod/reviews/todrdrev3.html |archivedate=2012-12-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/1999/02/13/tales-of-destiny-3 |title=Tales of Destiny |publisher=IGN |date= |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-date=2012-12-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Cz1rjNcB?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/1999/02/13/tales-of-destiny-3 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="IGNLegendia">{{Cite web |author=Dunham, Jeremy |title=Tales of Legendia |publisher=IGN |date=2006-02-07 |accessdate=2013-06-07 |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/02/08/tales-of-legendia?page=1 |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041856/https://www.ign.com/articles/2006/02/08/tales-of-legendia?page=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]]专门以《圣恩传说》为例，称線性動作戰鬥系統是五大顶尖JRPG战斗系统之一<ref name="GTjrpg">{{cite web|url=http://www.gametrailers.com/videos/07srt8/gt-countdown-top-5-jrpg-battle-systems|title=GT Countdown - Top 5 JRPG Battle Systems|publisher=[[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]]|date=2014-02-26|accessdate=2014-08-02|archive-date=2015-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122044314/http://www.gametrailers.com/videos/07srt8/gt-countdown-top-5-jrpg-battle-systems|dead-url=no}}</ref>。故事和角色多获西方褒贬两极的评价：《遗迹传说》、《深渊传说》和《无尽传说》的评价从褒贬不一到积极<ref name="IGNLegendia" /><ref name="1UPLegendia">{{cite web |last=Parish |first=Jeremy |url=http://www.1up.com/reviews/tales-of-legendia_2 |title=Tales of Legendia Review for PS2 |publisher=1UP.com |date=2006-02-07 |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archivedate=2013-04-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130422234111/http://www.1up.com/reviews/tales-of-legendia_2 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="GSpotLegendia">{{Cite web |last=Massimilla |first=Bethany |url=http://www.gamespot.com/tales-of-legendia/reviews/tales-of-legendia-review-6143743/ |title=Tales of Legendia Review |publisher=GameSpot |date=2006-02-06 |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2019-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629083903/https://www.gamespot.com/tales-of-legendia/reviews/tales-of-legendia-review-6143743/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="IGNAbyss">{{cite web |date=2006-10-11 |author=Haynes, Jeff |title=Tales of the Abyss Review |url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/738/738517p1.html |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2013-06-10 |archive-date=2012-05-10 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67XmisDUa?url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/738/738517p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="GRabyss">{{cite web |date=2006-10-06 |author=Nutt, Christian |title=Tales of the Abyss Review |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/us/ps2/game/reviews/article.jsp?articleId=20061005101921746038&sectionId=1000 |publisher=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]] |accessdate=2013-06-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/67XrP7N2F?url=http://www.gamesradar.com/tales-of-the-abyss-10/ |archivedate=2012-05-10 }}</ref><ref name="GSXilliareview">{{cite web| url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/tales-of-xillia-review/1900-6413799/| title=''Tales of Xillia'' review| first=Heidi| last=Kemps| date=2012-08-28| publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]| accessdate=2013-09-18| archive-date=2020-04-25| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041930/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/tales-of-xillia-review/1900-6413799/| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="GIXilliareview">{{cite web| url=http://www.gameinformer.com/games/tales_of_xillia/b/ps3/archive/2013/08/06/coming-back-stronger.aspx| title=''Tales of Xillia'' Review| first=Kimberley| last=Wallace| date=2013-08-06| publisher=''[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]''| accessdate=2013-08-06| archive-date=2020-04-25| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041936/https://www.gameinformer.com/games/tales_of_xillia/b/ps3/archive/2013/08/06/coming-back-stronger.aspx| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="IGNXilliareview">{{cite web| url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/08/06/tales-of-xillia-review| title=IGN ''Tales of Xillia'' Review| first=Colin| last=Moriarty| date=2013-08-05| publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]| accessdate=2013-08-05| archive-date=2020-11-12| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112023346/https://www.ign.com/articles/2013/08/06/tales-of-xillia-review| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="JoystiqXilliareview">{{cite web| url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/08/06/tales-of-xillia-review/| title=Tales of Xillia review| first=Susan| last=Arendt| date=2013-08-06| publisher=[[Joystiq|Joystiq]]| accessdate=2013-08-06| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128193228/http://www.joystiq.com/2013/08/06/tales-of-xillia-review/| archive-date=2015-01-28| dead-url=yes}}</ref>，《仙乐传说》和《圣恩传说》等则蒙受批评<ref name="GameSpotSymphreview">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/tales-of-symphonia-review/1900-6102021/ |title=GameSpot ''Tales of Symphonia'' review |last=Massimilla |first=Bethany |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2004-07-06 |accessdate=2012-05-15 |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041948/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/tales-of-symphonia-review/1900-6102021/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="IGNSymphreview">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/07/06/tales-of-symphonia-2 |title=IGN ''Tales of Symphonia'' review |last=Irwin |first=Mary Jane |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2006-07-04 |accessdate=2012-05-15 |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041957/https://www.ign.com/articles/2004/07/06/tales-of-symphonia-2 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="EurogamerSymphreview">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/r_TalesOfSymphonia_GC |title=Eurogamer ''Tales Of Symphonia'' Review |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |date=2004-11-02 |first=Rob |last=Fahey |accessdate=2012-05-15 |archive-date=2012-10-07 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BEJZYf3b?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/r_TalesOfSymphonia_GC |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="GIGracesreview">{{cite web |url=http://www.gameinformer.com/games/tales_of_graces_f/b/ps3/archive/2012/03/12/tales-of-graces-f-review-a-story-of-friendship-and-jrpg-clich-233-s.aspx |title=''Tales of Graces f'' Game Informer review |first=Kyle |last=Hilliard |date=2012-03-12 |publisher=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |accessdate=2012-05-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131115081603/http://www.gameinformer.com/games/tales_of_graces_f/b/ps3/archive/2012/03/12/tales-of-graces-f-review-a-story-of-friendship-and-jrpg-clich-233-s.aspx |archivedate=2013-11-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="GSpotGracesreview">{{cite web |url=http://uk.gamespot.com/tales-of-graces-f/reviews/tales-of-graces-f-review-6373244/ |title=''Tales of Graces f'' GameSpot review |first=Scott |last=Nichols |date=2012-04-24 |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2012-05-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120519031532/http://uk.gamespot.com/tales-of-graces-f/reviews/tales-of-graces-f-review-6373244/ |archivedate=2012-05-19 }}</ref><ref name="GRadarGracesreview">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/tales-of-graces-f-review/ |title=''Tales of Graces f'' GamesRadar review |first=Kimberley |last=Wallace |date=2012-03-13 |publisher=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]] |accessdate=2012-05-31 |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425042014/https://www.gamesradar.com/tales-of-graces-f-review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。对这些游戏和《遗迹传说》的批评是故事可以猜到或老生常谈<ref name="1UPLegendia" /><ref name="IGNSymphreview" /><ref name="GSpotGracesreview" />。系列几部游戏的图形也获得分化的评价，如《宿命传说》、《永恒传说》、《圣恩传说》和《无尽传说》<ref name="Joystiq review" /><ref name="IGNXilliareview" /><ref name="GSpotEternia">{{cite web |author=Shoemaker, Brad |url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/tales-of-destiny-ii-review/1900-2812486/ |title=Tales of Destiny II Review |publisher=GameSpot |date=2001-09-14 |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2014-08-18 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20140818230211/http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/tales-of-destiny-ii-review/1900-2812486/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="RPGreviewDestiny">{{cite web |url=http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/talesofdestiny/Tales_of_Destiny.html |title=RPGFan Reviews - Tales of Destiny |author=Esque |date=1998-10-23 |accessdate=2013-07-01 |publisher=RPGFan |archive-date=2012-12-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Cz1saGJu?url=http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/talesofdestiny/Tales_of_Destiny.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

随着2013年的《[[仙乐传说_同律包|仙乐传说 同律包]]》的发行，馬場称《仙乐传说》是系列到当时在西方最成功的作品，虽然系列主要目标受众仍在日本<ref name="DesBaba">{{cite web|url=http://www.destructoid.com/tales-producer-comments-on-symphonia-s-success-wii-u-251417.phtml|title=Tales producer comments on Symphonia's success, Wii U|author=Swiader, Keith|publisher=[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]|date=2013-12-04|accessdate=2014-08-01|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112040524/https://www.destructoid.com/tales-producer-comments-on-symphonia-s-success-wii-u-251417.phtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而马场在早期采访中称，为保持系列清新、同时在每作中沿用基本元素，系列幕后团队投入了大量精力和开发<ref name="GamaHistory" />。美国玩家对《仙乐传说》的积极反响影响了之后各个团队的游戏开发<ref name="GamaInterview" />。制作经理丹尼斯·李在2014年表示，系列自《仙乐传说》发行后知名度开始上升。南梦宫万代作为回应，注重将更多作品引入西方。他们关于未来开发或发行什么作品的研究，大多数都围绕在游戏大会和特别活动中，和传说系列爱好者直接对话展开<ref name="NamcoWestern">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2014/04/23/tales-rpgs-growing-west-says-bandai-namco/|title=Tales of RPGs Are Growing In The West Says Bandai Namco|author=Ward, Robert|publisher=Siliconera|date=2014-04-24|accessdate=2014-08-01|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629080041/https://www.siliconera.com/2014/04/23/tales-rpgs-growing-west-says-bandai-namco/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

